1
00:00:18,688 --> 00:00:19,808
(Anonymous Email
A new email. Please check.)

2
00:00:25,888 --> 00:00:27,008
(Don't ask who I am. I don't want
Ruoxi to die unjustly.)

3
00:00:29,024 --> 00:00:31,968
(Don't ask who I am. I don't want
Ruoxi to die unjustly.)

4
00:00:53,408 --> 00:00:54,128
Jiasheng,

5
00:00:55,289 --> 00:00:57,809
Mr. Tang considers us insiders.

6
00:00:58,529 --> 00:01:00,169
If we were outsiders

7
00:01:00,448 --> 00:01:01,969
standing him up twice,

8
00:01:02,969 --> 00:01:04,328
we'd never get another meeting.

9
00:01:05,569 --> 00:01:06,209
Mr. Tang,

10
00:01:06,768 --> 00:01:08,008
you're magnanimous,

11
00:01:08,728 --> 00:01:10,128
so we toast you.

12
00:01:19,048 --> 00:01:19,688
Mr. Tu,

13
00:01:20,249 --> 00:01:21,048
Mr. Zhao,

14
00:01:21,809 --> 00:01:23,009
what happened

15
00:01:23,009 --> 00:01:25,809
last time did anger Mr. Tang.

16
00:01:26,848 --> 00:01:28,568
They say third time's the charm,

17
00:01:28,969 --> 00:01:31,768
yet we keep coming with sincerity.

18
00:01:32,449 --> 00:01:33,729
You should at least

19
00:01:33,809 --> 00:01:35,369
offer something real.

20
00:01:42,729 --> 00:01:43,288
Jiasheng,

21
00:01:43,768 --> 00:01:45,408
they're demanding something real.

22
00:01:47,768 --> 00:01:48,488
Mr. Tang,

23
00:01:49,128 --> 00:01:50,688
I hear you're interested

24
00:01:50,688 --> 00:01:51,568
in joining ASEAN.

25
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:56,576
=The Glory Fades=

26
00:01:57,312 --> 00:01:59,616
=Episode 20=
(Tamed)

27
00:02:01,529 --> 00:02:02,809
I received

28
00:02:03,048 --> 00:02:04,128
a mysterious email.

29
00:02:06,089 --> 00:02:07,288
Wearing lipstick now.

30
00:02:18,209 --> 00:02:19,168
Mr. Tu,

31
00:02:19,369 --> 00:02:21,688
don't mock me.

32
00:02:23,369 --> 00:02:24,769
I'm merely

33
00:02:24,769 --> 00:02:27,249
a deputy governor.

34
00:02:27,969 --> 00:02:29,049
ASEAN membership

35
00:02:29,049 --> 00:02:30,489
is light-years away.

36
00:02:30,489 --> 00:02:31,288
Bottoms up.

37
00:02:50,249 --> 00:02:51,608
Mr. Tang,

38
00:02:51,848 --> 00:02:53,168
good evening.

39
00:02:53,288 --> 00:02:53,888
Today

40
00:02:53,888 --> 00:02:55,688
I've brought two familiar faces.

41
00:03:00,008 --> 00:03:01,089
Miss Yingwan

42
00:03:01,369 --> 00:03:03,688
composed poetry with you last time.

43
00:03:03,688 --> 00:03:04,688
Remember her?

44
00:03:06,089 --> 00:03:07,089
And this,

45
00:03:07,168 --> 00:03:08,969
Su Yunian,

46
00:03:08,969 --> 00:03:11,249
last beauty contest's champion.

47
00:03:13,249 --> 00:03:14,249
Good evening, Mr. Tang.

48
00:03:14,408 --> 00:03:16,209
Two drinkers facing mountain blooms,

49
00:03:16,209 --> 00:03:17,769
cup after cup.

50
00:03:17,809 --> 00:03:19,008
Pleased to meet again.

51
00:03:19,089 --> 00:03:19,688
Good.

52
00:03:19,688 --> 00:03:20,888
Li Bai's poetry.

53
00:03:21,249 --> 00:03:21,929
Excellent.

54
00:03:23,128 --> 00:03:24,168
Mr. Tang, good evening.

55
00:03:24,489 --> 00:03:25,529
We first met

56
00:03:25,529 --> 00:03:27,529
at your inauguration.

57
00:03:27,809 --> 00:03:29,089
Every word you spoke

58
00:03:29,089 --> 00:03:30,329
made me realize

59
00:03:30,529 --> 00:03:31,448
the weight behind

60
00:03:31,448 --> 00:03:33,489
your rise to power

61
00:03:33,568 --> 00:03:35,728
and your limitless potential.

62
00:03:35,728 --> 00:03:37,249
Hope you enjoy tonight.

63
00:03:40,408 --> 00:03:41,568
What happened to your hand?

64
00:03:43,209 --> 00:03:45,769
Got hurt opening wine recently.

65
00:03:46,529 --> 00:03:48,049
I was off-duty today,

66
00:03:48,329 --> 00:03:49,848
but hearing you'd come,

67
00:03:50,049 --> 00:03:51,249
and Mr. Tu values me

68
00:03:51,249 --> 00:03:52,249
and especially you,

69
00:03:52,369 --> 00:03:54,529
so I reported despite injury.

70
00:03:54,649 --> 00:03:55,848
Hope you don't mind.

71
00:03:56,089 --> 00:03:56,769
Not at all.

72
00:03:56,769 --> 00:03:58,369
Miss Su, please sit.

73
00:03:58,568 --> 00:03:59,249
You

74
00:03:59,529 --> 00:04:00,929
should sit by Mr. Tu.

75
00:04:02,168 --> 00:04:03,168
Since you're here,

76
00:04:03,168 --> 00:04:04,369
I'll attend to you.

77
00:04:04,649 --> 00:04:06,288
Mr. Tu won't mind.

78
00:04:06,888 --> 00:04:08,128
Right, Mr. Tu?

79
00:04:18,168 --> 00:04:19,489
Mr. Tang,

80
00:04:19,688 --> 00:04:20,688
a toast to you.

81
00:04:20,688 --> 00:04:21,529
But...

82
00:04:26,529 --> 00:04:27,288
You're injured.

83
00:04:27,769 --> 00:04:28,368
Don't drink.

84
00:04:30,009 --> 00:04:30,889
Tang, see?

85
00:04:31,168 --> 00:04:33,129
How considerate Mr. Tu is.

86
00:04:33,129 --> 00:04:34,288
He truly cares for us.

87
00:04:34,288 --> 00:04:34,889
I'll empty

88
00:04:34,889 --> 00:04:36,529
my glass. Help yourself.

89
00:04:44,048 --> 00:04:44,848
Yunian,

90
00:04:46,168 --> 00:04:47,009
with this wine,

91
00:04:47,209 --> 00:04:48,408
I toast Mr. Tang.

92
00:04:49,728 --> 00:04:50,368
Mr. Tang,

93
00:04:50,728 --> 00:04:52,089
welcome once more

94
00:04:52,408 --> 00:04:54,689
to Deep In The Bustle.

95
00:05:10,689 --> 00:05:13,089
(That night rescuing Su Yunian,)

96
00:05:14,209 --> 00:05:16,808
(what did Mr. Tu's words really mean?)

97
00:05:29,449 --> 00:05:30,248
Bai Manni,

98
00:05:31,368 --> 00:05:32,488
I have a new shirt.

99
00:05:32,488 --> 00:05:33,288
Change her into it.

100
00:05:33,288 --> 00:05:33,848
Okay.

101
00:05:35,048 --> 00:05:36,009
Chu Bai, step out first.

102
00:05:36,009 --> 00:05:37,009
Leave this to me.

103
00:05:51,969 --> 00:05:52,569
Mr. Tu,

104
00:05:53,449 --> 00:05:55,248
it's inconvenient to leave her here.

105
00:05:55,368 --> 00:05:56,529
And it disturbs your rest.

106
00:05:56,808 --> 00:05:59,928
- Otherwise I should...
- Worried it's another trap?

107
00:06:01,569 --> 00:06:02,168
No.

108
00:06:02,329 --> 00:06:03,848
Room 999 is the safest.

109
00:06:04,488 --> 00:06:05,288
I just...

110
00:06:07,168 --> 00:06:08,009
You like her.

111
00:06:15,529 --> 00:06:16,329
Don't worry.

112
00:06:16,928 --> 00:06:18,168
I'll take good care of her.

113
00:06:21,808 --> 00:06:22,808
Thank you, Mr. Tu.

114
00:06:23,728 --> 00:06:24,368
Chu Bai.

115
00:06:25,368 --> 00:06:26,089
Chu Bai.

116
00:06:27,009 --> 00:06:28,009
What's wrong with you?

117
00:06:29,368 --> 00:06:30,009
Nothing.

118
00:06:30,728 --> 00:06:31,368
Nothing.

119
00:06:42,769 --> 00:06:43,329
Hello.

120
00:06:43,529 --> 00:06:44,728
You're Chu Bai, right?

121
00:06:45,408 --> 00:06:46,288
Who are you?

122
00:06:46,288 --> 00:06:48,009
You don't need to know who I am.

123
00:06:48,288 --> 00:06:49,769
I just want to ask you,

124
00:06:49,769 --> 00:06:51,488
if you see the girl you love

125
00:06:51,488 --> 00:06:52,969
holding someone else's arm,

126
00:06:53,449 --> 00:06:54,769
how would you feel?

127
00:06:57,368 --> 00:06:58,168
Are you crazy?

128
00:06:58,769 --> 00:06:59,728
I'll hang up.

129
00:06:59,969 --> 00:07:01,728
You can hang up on me,

130
00:07:01,889 --> 00:07:02,969
but I want to tell you

131
00:07:03,529 --> 00:07:05,248
that your beloved Su Yunian

132
00:07:05,529 --> 00:07:09,769
has moved into Tu Jiasheng's Room 999
on the second floor.

133
00:07:10,129 --> 00:07:11,129
And I

134
00:07:11,129 --> 00:07:13,848
have a way
to make her leave Tu Jiasheng,

135
00:07:15,168 --> 00:07:16,928
as long as you do what I say.

136
00:07:17,889 --> 00:07:19,248
I've emailed you

137
00:07:19,368 --> 00:07:21,089
the time and place.

138
00:07:21,728 --> 00:07:22,569
I'll be waiting.

139
00:07:36,529 --> 00:07:37,408
Mr. Tang,

140
00:07:38,129 --> 00:07:39,488
this is my sincerity.

141
00:07:39,928 --> 00:07:40,928
It's also

142
00:07:41,048 --> 00:07:42,488
Deep In The Bustle's sincerity.

143
00:07:43,449 --> 00:07:44,329
Bottoms up!

144
00:07:58,248 --> 00:08:00,969
Now you see what a heroine looks like.

145
00:08:02,129 --> 00:08:02,769
You

146
00:08:02,769 --> 00:08:03,889
need more training.

147
00:08:03,889 --> 00:08:05,288
Yes, Mr. Tang.

148
00:08:05,569 --> 00:08:06,368
Um...

149
00:08:07,329 --> 00:08:08,769
I need to use the restroom.

150
00:08:17,889 --> 00:08:18,649
Mr. Tang,

151
00:08:18,649 --> 00:08:19,728
we'll drink with you.

152
00:08:19,728 --> 00:08:20,649
Come on.

153
00:08:25,209 --> 00:08:25,928
Tang,

154
00:08:27,248 --> 00:08:28,129
excuse me.

155
00:08:29,288 --> 00:08:30,969
Where are you going, Mr. Tu?

156
00:08:31,048 --> 00:08:31,689
Don't mind him.

157
00:08:32,608 --> 00:08:33,529
Let's keep drinking.

158
00:08:33,969 --> 00:08:34,469
Okay.

159
00:08:45,008 --> 00:08:46,329
I brought you back to work

160
00:08:46,528 --> 00:08:48,329
to keep you within my sight,

161
00:08:48,648 --> 00:08:50,209
not for you to show off.

162
00:08:51,689 --> 00:08:52,488
Show off?

163
00:08:55,089 --> 00:08:56,528
I don't need to show off.

164
00:08:58,169 --> 00:08:59,089
Besides,

165
00:08:59,089 --> 00:09:00,329
I'm Madam now.

166
00:09:01,209 --> 00:09:02,089
I can't exactly

167
00:09:02,528 --> 00:09:03,888
embarrass you.

168
00:09:04,209 --> 00:09:05,169
When I need to puke,

169
00:09:05,689 --> 00:09:07,608
I even use another VIP room.

170
00:09:08,248 --> 00:09:09,528
I made you Madam

171
00:09:09,528 --> 00:09:10,848
to uncover the truth,

172
00:09:11,329 --> 00:09:12,809
not to degrade yourself.

173
00:09:13,569 --> 00:09:14,449
The truth?

174
00:09:16,528 --> 00:09:18,008
Really want me to find the truth?

175
00:09:19,689 --> 00:09:20,929
That day,

176
00:09:21,648 --> 00:09:24,169
was what you said on the rooftop

177
00:09:24,528 --> 00:09:25,969
really the whole truth?

178
00:09:27,209 --> 00:09:28,089
I'm afraid

179
00:09:28,368 --> 00:09:30,049
you're hiding a lot.

180
00:09:34,648 --> 00:09:35,289
Forget it.

181
00:09:36,209 --> 00:09:37,569
Let's go back to Room 999 first.

182
00:09:38,128 --> 00:09:38,929
Room 999?

183
00:09:40,888 --> 00:09:41,689
No need.

184
00:09:42,248 --> 00:09:42,848
Stop!

185
00:09:43,248 --> 00:09:44,569
Back to Room 999 first.

186
00:09:46,169 --> 00:09:48,289
I'm going back to Mr. Tang.

187
00:09:49,768 --> 00:09:51,248
Tu Jiasheng,

188
00:09:51,248 --> 00:09:52,248
what are you doing?

189
00:09:52,569 --> 00:09:53,768
Let go!

190
00:09:55,329 --> 00:09:56,728
Tu Jiasheng,

191
00:09:57,848 --> 00:09:59,089
let go!

192
00:10:09,848 --> 00:10:11,289
Tu Jiasheng,

193
00:10:11,289 --> 00:10:12,449
let me go!

194
00:10:12,809 --> 00:10:13,848
Hurry up!

195
00:10:14,528 --> 00:10:16,169
Are you crazy, Tu Jiasheng?

196
00:10:17,488 --> 00:10:19,089
I'm dizzy.

197
00:10:19,409 --> 00:10:20,289
I'm going to throw up.

198
00:10:20,569 --> 00:10:22,049
Enough, stop pretending.

199
00:10:26,528 --> 00:10:27,728
How do you know that?

200
00:10:28,728 --> 00:10:29,848
Because I

201
00:10:29,929 --> 00:10:31,689
asked the waiter to switch your wine

202
00:10:31,689 --> 00:10:32,768
to a soft drink.

203
00:10:35,169 --> 00:10:35,969
Thank you.

204
00:10:38,128 --> 00:10:39,169
Well,

205
00:10:39,329 --> 00:10:40,848
aren't you overacting?

206
00:10:41,049 --> 00:10:41,969
Throwing up is fine.

207
00:10:41,969 --> 00:10:43,169
But you flailed around wildly.

208
00:10:43,648 --> 00:10:44,329
And,

209
00:10:44,488 --> 00:10:45,368
you even bit me.

210
00:10:46,128 --> 00:10:47,528
You deserved that bite.

211
00:10:47,969 --> 00:10:48,888
Tu Jiasheng,

212
00:10:49,289 --> 00:10:50,329
after so many days here,

213
00:10:50,329 --> 00:10:51,528
I've finally realized.

214
00:10:51,608 --> 00:10:53,089
Those you wine and dine

215
00:10:53,089 --> 00:10:54,329
outranks the last,

216
00:10:54,608 --> 00:10:57,248
like mayors, governors,
Cabinet members, ASEAN officials,

217
00:10:57,248 --> 00:10:58,848
each more influential than the other.

218
00:10:58,848 --> 00:10:59,648
Yet when it comes

219
00:10:59,648 --> 00:11:01,569
to the police's
so-called scapegoat theory,

220
00:11:01,569 --> 00:11:03,128
you're indifferent. Silent and passive.

221
00:11:03,608 --> 00:11:04,409
I've been waiting

222
00:11:04,969 --> 00:11:06,449
for a reasonable explanation.

223
00:11:06,608 --> 00:11:08,008
I told you I have my reasons.

224
00:11:08,008 --> 00:11:09,929
Yes, you have your reasons.

225
00:11:10,169 --> 00:11:11,209
The reason is you

226
00:11:11,528 --> 00:11:13,368
can't exactly send yourself to prison.

227
00:11:13,848 --> 00:11:14,768
Will you ever stop?

228
00:11:14,768 --> 00:11:15,528
No, I won't.

229
00:11:15,768 --> 00:11:17,728
I won't rest until I uncover the truth

230
00:11:17,728 --> 00:11:18,689
and avenge Ruoxi.

231
00:11:19,089 --> 00:11:20,008
Childish.

232
00:11:20,329 --> 00:11:21,008
Correct.

233
00:11:21,209 --> 00:11:22,449
I'm childish,

234
00:11:22,648 --> 00:11:23,888
not as shrewd as you

235
00:11:23,888 --> 00:11:25,008
with many connections.

236
00:11:25,049 --> 00:11:26,528
At worst, I'll die and join her.

237
00:11:26,848 --> 00:11:28,969
Otherwise, nothing will stop me.

238
00:11:29,209 --> 00:11:30,728
No one's stopping you.

239
00:11:31,289 --> 00:11:32,608
But we need coordination.

240
00:11:33,528 --> 00:11:34,169
Fine.

241
00:11:34,728 --> 00:11:35,329
Tell me.

242
00:11:35,608 --> 00:11:36,528
How do we coordinate?

243
00:11:38,169 --> 00:11:40,209
Remember what we said on the rooftop?

244
00:11:40,569 --> 00:11:41,608
We must work together.

245
00:11:41,809 --> 00:11:42,329
You,

246
00:11:42,689 --> 00:11:43,689
play Madam.

247
00:12:42,888 --> 00:12:45,128
- Good evening, Mr. Tu, Madam.
- Good evening, Mr. Tu, Madam.

248
00:12:50,089 --> 00:12:51,329
Chu Bai,

249
00:12:51,648 --> 00:12:52,689
what are you doing here?

250
00:12:52,888 --> 00:12:53,528
Waiting for you.

251
00:12:53,748 --> 00:12:54,248
Here.

252
00:12:54,248 --> 00:12:54,969
Same old thing.

253
00:12:55,209 --> 00:12:55,848
Alright.

254
00:12:58,209 --> 00:12:58,969
Say it.

255
00:13:02,528 --> 00:13:03,449
Say what?

256
00:13:04,528 --> 00:13:05,969
Say whatever you want.

257
00:13:10,089 --> 00:13:11,329
You are dating

258
00:13:12,289 --> 00:13:13,209
Tu Jiasheng?

259
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:14,089
You're about to become

260
00:13:14,528 --> 00:13:15,569
the new Madam?

261
00:13:15,569 --> 00:13:16,488
Is it true?

262
00:13:20,049 --> 00:13:21,488
Do you wish it were true?

263
00:13:26,089 --> 00:13:26,929
No.

264
00:13:30,209 --> 00:13:32,329
Remember what we said on the rooftop?

265
00:13:32,768 --> 00:13:33,768
We must work together.

266
00:13:33,929 --> 00:13:34,528
You,

267
00:13:34,648 --> 00:13:35,569
play Madam.

268
00:13:36,248 --> 00:13:37,049
Su Yunian!

269
00:13:39,089 --> 00:13:39,888
Su Yunian!

270
00:13:40,809 --> 00:13:41,449
Su Yunian!

271
00:13:41,929 --> 00:13:42,768
What's wrong?

272
00:13:43,728 --> 00:13:44,528
Nothing.

273
00:13:45,089 --> 00:13:46,008
What did you say?

274
00:13:47,608 --> 00:13:48,528
I asked

275
00:13:49,449 --> 00:13:52,248
if you're really dating Tu Jiasheng.

276
00:13:53,768 --> 00:13:54,368
Yes.

277
00:13:55,008 --> 00:13:55,809
Just last night.

278
00:14:05,888 --> 00:14:06,608
Why?

279
00:14:08,329 --> 00:14:09,128
For money.

280
00:14:09,768 --> 00:14:11,248
He's wealthy, powerful

281
00:14:11,409 --> 00:14:12,528
and handsome.

282
00:14:13,089 --> 00:14:15,528
Though he's over a decade older,

283
00:14:15,528 --> 00:14:17,008
that's hardly an issue.

284
00:14:17,329 --> 00:14:18,329
Satisfied with my answer?

285
00:14:22,089 --> 00:14:22,728
Yes.

286
00:14:23,008 --> 00:14:23,969
Brutally honest.

287
00:14:24,728 --> 00:14:25,329
I...

288
00:14:26,848 --> 00:14:27,689
I didn't expect this.

289
00:14:30,008 --> 00:14:30,969
Neither did I.

290
00:14:34,008 --> 00:14:34,648
Alright.

291
00:14:35,569 --> 00:14:36,488
If nothing else,

292
00:14:36,488 --> 00:14:37,449
I'll leave.

293
00:14:43,648 --> 00:14:44,449
Su Yunian.

294
00:14:57,528 --> 00:14:58,329
Take care.

295
00:15:02,752 --> 00:15:06,880
♪Even the starlight has dimmed♪

296
00:15:08,768 --> 00:15:11,820
♪Leaving only me behind♪

297
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:15,872
♪Awake alone♪

298
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:21,696
♪What will tomorrow bring♪

299
00:15:24,953 --> 00:15:28,640
♪Perhaps I was wrong♪

300
00:15:32,288 --> 00:15:37,739
♪Finally saying it out loud brings
some relief♪

301
00:15:38,496 --> 00:15:41,345
♪I only wanted to play♪

302
00:15:42,304 --> 00:15:44,864
♪The role you loved♪

303
00:15:45,184 --> 00:15:52,768
♪Even if the ending is too bitter♪

304
00:15:55,371 --> 00:15:58,624
♪Turns out I would cry♪

305
00:15:59,072 --> 00:16:02,272
♪Turns out you would hurt♪

306
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:10,272
♪Those rights and wrongs from the past
don't matter anymore♪

307
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:18,219
♪How much I miss the joy
we once shared together♪

308
00:16:18,432 --> 00:16:24,630
♪If only we could go back to the past♪

309
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:28,224
♪Perhaps at this very moment♪

310
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:32,175
♪I can finally understand♪

311
00:16:32,352 --> 00:16:39,744
♪What to love and hate
are all my choices♪

312
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:42,816
♪Some words I don't say♪

313
00:16:42,944 --> 00:16:47,798
♪Doesn't mean I no longer care♪

314
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:54,249
♪I just wish to hear 'I love you'
one more time♪

315
00:17:02,209 --> 00:17:03,528
Hello, this is Chu Bai.

316
00:17:06,929 --> 00:17:07,936
Tell me what to do.

317
00:17:15,584 --> 00:17:19,258
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

318
00:17:19,557 --> 00:17:22,748
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

319
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:28,201
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

320
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:31,744
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

321
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:36,750
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

322
00:17:36,974 --> 00:17:40,471
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

323
00:17:41,870 --> 00:17:45,557
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

324
00:17:46,195 --> 00:17:51,310
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

325
00:17:52,014 --> 00:17:56,148
♪I feel guilty♪

326
00:17:56,718 --> 00:18:00,462
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

327
00:18:01,326 --> 00:18:04,769
♪Even in tears♪

328
00:18:05,518 --> 00:18:09,432
♪It doesn't matter♪

329
00:18:09,614 --> 00:18:13,437
♪We embrace in dreams♪

330
00:18:14,286 --> 00:18:17,724
♪I let down all my defenses♪

331
00:18:18,958 --> 00:18:22,321
♪Though the story has its end♪

332
00:18:23,086 --> 00:18:30,560
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
